data.description: Welcome home! Adorable 3 bed/2 bath ranch in Cambridge with easy access to 485. Fantastic amenities including a community pool, recreational area and playground. This beauty boasts a large amount of natural light. Amazing floorpan that is wonderful for hosting celebrations. Cozy up in front of the fire with a good book on cool winter nights. Updated countertops, cabinets, stainless steel appliances and lots of storage in the kitchen. Spacious primary suite with double sinks and a walk-in closet. Covered back patio is a little piece of serenity that opens up to a large wooded area. New HVAC and tankless water heater in 2021, new disposal and stove 2022. This home has a lot of love to give!
